Package fi.abo.kogni.soile2.datamanagement.git

Class GitDataRetriever<T>

java.lang.Object
fi.abo.kogni.soile2.datamanagement.git.GitDataRetriever<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of data this retriever provides.
All Implemented Interfaces:
DataRetriever<GitFile,T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
DataLakeResourceManager, ObjectManager
public abstract class GitDataRetriever<T> extends Object implements DataRetriever<GitFile,T>
This abstract class provides a general implementation of a DataRetriever for gitFiles and a target object. It needs to know whether the retrieved Data is Json or String.
Author:
Thomas Pfau
